Value Key        Short Description
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
BANNER           Fixed Top Banner
TOAST            Toast Notification (5s)
BOTH             Banner + Toast
SILENT           Silent (Log Only)

*-- Notes:
*   Display Mode Controls:
*     BANNER: Traditional fixed banner at top, user must close
*     TOAST: Bottom-right toast, auto-dismiss after 5 seconds
*     BOTH: Shows both banner and toast simultaneously
*     SILENT: Logged only, no UI display (audit trail via /log endpoint)
*
*   Default: BANNER (for backward compatibility)
*
*   Use Cases:
*     BANNER: Critical system messages requiring acknowledgment
*     TOAST: Non-intrusive informational updates
*     BOTH: Important messages that need visibility + persistence
*     SILENT: Background notifications for audit/compliance
